<plot>Spanning the last 3 years of British rule (1994-1997), this documentary series paints a vivid picture of the city and its politics through a cross-section of citizens: democratic activists, leading politicians, media tycoons, millionaire entrepreneurs, expatriates, dissidents, and ordinary families. It provides a unique insight into their hopes, dreams and fears as they adapt and change in the face of an uncertain future.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?463329</url></doc>
